{"tid":2461814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"路透：日本無印良品母公司稱“非常關切”中國新疆強制勞動報導","createTime":"2021-03-25T14:49:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T14:56:34.000Z","uid":333287,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"67a1662bfd3553cb7b18c0e853b76ae223374a5e","tid":2461814,"uid":333287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T14:49:48.000Z","msg":"路透東京3月25日- 經營無印良品品牌的日本良品計劃週四表示，&ldquo;非常關切&rdquo;中國新疆地區強制勞動的報導。<br />\n<br />\n良品計劃發表聲明稱，公司已對供應產品的新疆工廠進行查核，稱發現明顯問題。良品計劃表示，正在設法確保合乎歐盟及美國有關新疆人權的法律及規範。(完)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/japan-muji-xinjiang-cotton-0325-idCNKBS2BH1LQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fjapan-muji-xinjiang-cotton-0325-idCNKBS2BH1LQ&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2Fjv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=d3c43368\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fjapan-muji-xinjiang-cotton-0325-idCNKBS2BH1LQ&h=23ef2e82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/japan-muji-xinjiang-cotton-0325-idCNKBS2BH1LQ</a><br />\n<br />\n又要抵制了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b482ee2deb84f859d1e8907f43f1403a46f61b46","tid":2461814,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T14:52:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfHhkypGbd64ZtLFkpnL456svSu1sJVvNFxusstSn1KoB?filename=ygj3qTA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fygj3qTA.jpg&h=c2e8b100&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYpcW95ShQjG7zt9UFGSgTz3bX63iwwLcvjZX9eWGeSNH?filename=sQAieMX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsQAieMX.jpg&h=09235c87&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUk4y2hjgM3W5YNtEkXAzRY73V8oqxZ3hdyo1y